background 
on september  we announced that we were reviewing certain accounting practices and previously reported financial statements as a result of possible errors discovered by our management in the accounting for software development costs and project capitalization and other project cost capitalization accounting practices at our dids business unit 
on november   we announced that we were delaying the filing of our form q for the third quarter ended september  due to our ongoing evaluation of certain accounting issues relating to transactions entered into in prior periods 
