in the case of estimates  prior to publicly reporting results  our practice is to compare the actual production volumes to estimated production volumes and adjust revenue amounts as necessary 
however  for the first and second quarters of  this practice was not followed and  as a result  we understated revenues during the first quarter of and overstated revenues for the second quarter of other adjustments 
